text:
### Content library

You can enable the integration with Go1 Content Hub to enrich the learning
resources that you can browse for the courses from the MaivenPoint interfaces.
To use this feature, navigate to the **Settings** > **Content library** to
turn on the switch for Go1 and enable the integration.
